  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to compare 2 different hemostatic agents (Bonewax and Ostene)to
      a control group with regards to bleeding, bone healing, pain and infection in a patient group
      all undergoing median sternotomy.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
