  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  men undergoing elective cardiac surgery at the Cardiac surgery department of Aarhus
             University Hospital, Skejby

          -  no clopidogrel-treatment

          -  no osteoporoses

          -  less than 2 co-morbidities in the form of obesity (BMI&gt;30), COPD, chronic steroid use,
             renal failure, immunosuppression and diabetes

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  profuse sternal bleeding

          -  serious complications to the surgery fx cerebral infarction

          -  re-operation due to bleeding
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
